                        CE</origDate>.</origin>
                  <provenance>
                     <p>While the circumstances under which this volume arrived in <placeName
                           ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/70111987008653" key="place_7008653"
                           >Britain</placeName> remain unclear, <persName role="fmo"
